schools.name: Woodlawn High Center For Pre-Eng. Res.

data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Woodlawn, Maryland! This stunning 4-bedroom single-family residence offers an exceptional blend of modern elegance and timeless charm.  Step into a spacious haven with gleaming hardwood floors that stretch throughout, creating a seamless flow from room to room. The updated kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, boasting sleek stainless steel appliances, perfect for creating culinary masterpieces. With its open concept design, the kitchen seamlessly merges into the living area, ideal for entertaining guests or enjoying family gatherings.  Experience comfort and luxury in the updated bathrooms, designed with sophistication and functionality in mind. The four spacious bedrooms provide ample space for relaxation and personalization, ensuring everyone has their private oasis.  Outside, the home sits on a generous lot, providing a large yard that invites endless possibilities – from creating your own outdoor sanctuary to hosting delightful gatherings under the open sky.  Nestled in the charming community of Woodlawn, this property offers convenience and tranquility, with easy access to local amenities, schools, and transportation.  Don't miss the chance to make this exquisite residence your own – where modern amenities meet classic elegance in a coveted neighborhood setting.
